name: Maneuvering Flaps (V)
Lore: 'Enhanced steering mechanisms on Rebel T-47s provide increased maneuverability in planetary atmospheres.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. During your deploy phase, may reveal an unpiloted combat vehicle from hand to take its matching pilot character (or vice versa) from Reserve Deck and deploy both simultaneously; reshuffle. May not be suspended (Immune to Alter.)',
